how to run:

$ g++ NetworkSim.cpp BaseStation.cpp Node.cpp -o Networksim && ./NetworkSim


Project Name: Wireless network simulator
Description: A secondary wireless network simulator.

Dependencies:
    g++
    Python 3.7
    matplotlib
    numpy

To install Python3 dependencies, type in commandline:
    * For matplotlib:
        pip install matplotlib
        
    * For numpy:
        pip install numpy